While attempting to seek help from the century of Super Heroes, they find themselves locked out of time and discover a clue to who is behind the forces terrorizing their homes.

description:
Massawa, Eritrea. Italian colony, year 1889:

Ugo Pastore reluctantly accompanies his father Enea, trade official of the Caput Mundi Company, in Eritrea. Enea intends to expand the activities of the company guaranteeing the supply of a good portion of provisions to the Italian army stationed in the place. The honest business man, however, aims to broaden the influence of the company and establish business relations with the King of Ethiopia, Menelik II.
name: I predoni del deserto

description: 1894. In Rome, Ugo has a new job: he's employed by a notary who administers the fortunes of many important families. One evening, returning home, he is attacked by a bunch of street thugs. Vittorio De Cesari, a cavalry officer, defends him sword in hand and chases away the bad guys. Between Vittorio and Ugo a deep friendship rises. The officer is the young scion of a noble family who owns an estate in the Roman Castles. Vittorio chooses Ugo as its administrator.
name: Briganti

description:
The Italian government prepares to send more troops to Africa, and Vittorio is among the candidates to go.
Matilde, frightened by this prospect, tryes to convince General Orsini, in charge of drawing up the starting order, not to include Vittorio on the list . Ugo, albeit reluctantly, agrees to help her by making an uninhabited house available for the meeting. But the clandestine meeting between Matilda and Orsini do not get the desired result and has tragic consequences ...
name: Amore e morte

description: Soon after arriving in Africa, Vittorio, believing that the Abyssinians know the territory better and are better fighters of the Italians, constitutes a special division of cavalry, composed entirely of native troops. In the dramatic context of the battle Amba Alagi, disastrous for the Italian army, Vittorio and his men stand out for the decisiveness of their actions. But on the path of retreat, they come across Volto Nascosto, together with the Queen of Ethiopia, Taytu.
name: Volto Nascosto

description: After successfully protected the Italian retreat, Vittorio fled to Macallé where the troops of General Arimondi are leaving the Fortress, an Italian stronghold, abandoning the defense to a handful of men. Vittorio, leading his department of indigenous soldiers, fights like a lion, but the overwhelming Abyssinian forces shake the Fortress from all sides and Volto Nascosto conquers the water springs, cutting off water supplies to the besieged ...
name: La Fortezza

description: While the brave resistance of the Italian soldiers besieged in Macallé continues, Vittorio and his squad are sent to the headquartersto call for reinforcements, but the raiders of Volto Nascosto are on their path. Between Vittorio and the legendary silver masked warrior begins a duel to the death ...
name: Gli eroi di Makallé

description: Matilde withdrew in Vittorio's country house awaiting his return, but even here she can not find peace. The ghost of General Orsini, stabbed by her, haunts her. Is this only a nightmare born from his sick imagination or is there something real in these frightening apparitions?
name: Il fantasma

description: Collecting the status quo altering storyline "A DIFFERENT WORLD" running from issues 25-30. Mark is brought to another planet in order to save it. Is he their only hope - or the source of the worst disaster to ever befall them?
name: Volume Six

description: Ugo is back to Massawa looking for news of Vittorio, now a prisoner of Volto Nascosto. He learns that a great battle is preparing in Adua and tries to reach the area by joining the small caravan of Duke Pandolfi, personal envoy of King Umberto I. But along the way are two predators ambush him, Agos Sebath and Ras Tafari, once allies of the Italians and now passed to the enemy ...
name: La strada per Adua

description: On a trip to Africa Mark finds himself torn between two lives; his normal life with his girlfriend Amber and his superhero life with good friend Atom Eve. Decisions, decisions... Also in this volume: Angstrom Levy makes his move and the truth about ROBOT is revealed!
name: Volume Seven

description: Invincible battles the REANIMEN on the campus of Upstate University. Meanwhile, unbeknownst to him trouble is brewing - trouble of MARTIAN origin. Invincible must assemble a team of Earth's mightiest defenders to go out into space and prevent what could well be the end of mankind!
name: Volume Eight

description:
A new era begins with the debut of the oversized, monthly BATMAN BEYOND UNLIMITED, featuring the print debut of the new Justice League Beyond!

In the Batman Beyond chapter, legendary Batman artist Norm Breyfogle returns to draw the Dark Knight of the future with best-selling writer Adam Beechen. In "10,000 Clowns," an onslaught of new Jokerz is plaguing Gotham City – and the implications of this chaotic clown menace could have disastrous consequences for Terry McGinnis and Bruce Wayne!

And the debut of the Justice League Beyond is here, courtesy of the BATMAN: STREETS OF GOTHAM art team of Dustin Nguyen and Derek Fridolfs, as the first two digital-first chapters are available in print for the first time! Batman Beyond is a new recruit in the mighty Justice League, but the team will be immediately tested by a very Neo Gotham-related enemy! How will the team work together to combat this threat?
name: 10,000 Clowns (Prelude); Konstriction, Chapter 1: A Snake In The Grass

description:
He's back!! And he's doin' it old school!!

After a hard fought battle, WEIRD PETE has stepped behind the GM SHIELD and BACK into the SADDLE.

and he's bringing HELL with him...

The question is -- will his PLAYERS survive?
name: (2 of 2)

volume.name: Knights of the Dinner Table: Black Hands 2010 Special

description:
It's war in MUNCIE...

A new live action game has hit Muncie, and the knights are in the middle of it!! Armed with paint ball guns, it's gamer vs. gamer as they hunt each other down. The goal? To be the last man standing. This original self contained story has it all - intrigue, betrayal, and laughs. From Weird Pete's back room, to back alleys, to the open gaming room at Garycon itself. No one is safe. Don't turn your back. Don't trust your friends. And for gawd's sake -- save the last paint ball for yourself!
name: Last Man Standing

description: What did Batman expect to find on his Odyssey to the Underworld? So far it's been nothing but tragedy. Once The Dark Knight took the first step, the world he knew was gone. Will Batman become the thing he most loathes: a murderer? Each step takes him closer...
name: Part 11

description: All phases of the tragic battle of Adwa between Italian troops and the army of Menelik. Volto Nascosto fights like a lion. Ugo, escaped the surveillance of Bathos, reaches the site of the battle too late. Meanwhile, the news about the fate of his friend Vittorio, are extremely worrying.
name: Pioggia di Sangue
